yle=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">N</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Y</strong></span></span><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">OU</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>S</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">PURS</span></span><img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/797/Oyk0dK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F797%2FOyk0dK.gif&h=edd86a2d&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C-gweZ7XcAAPBJ9.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC-gweZ7XcAAPBJ9.jpg%3Alarge&h=6ef3569e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/02/001639_0926604e6c2d44f106dcc1d57d418370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F02%2F001639_0926604e6c2d44f106dcc1d57d418370.jpg&h=01a38c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">熱刺</span></span></strong>是一間座落英國倫敦北部托定咸區的職業足球會<br />\n從1882年成立至今已經擁有過千年歷史，現時競逐於英格蘭超級聯賽；<br />\n球會主場為白鹿徑球場，球會的拉丁文格言 &rdquo;<em>Audere est Facere (To Dare Is To Do)</em>&rdquo; 則意謂「<em>屌柒獌聯</em>」</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/uploadedImages/Shared_Assets/Images/History/Honours/league_champions_1951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tottenhamhotspur.com%2FuploadedImages%2FShared_Assets%2FImages%2FHistory%2FHonours%2Fleague_champions_1951.jpg&h=6a1de3c7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http:/